---
title: Chicken and Potato Hash with Spring Greens and Apple
description: Our chicken and potato hash is an uncomplicated dish brimming with flavour, like delicate garlic, bold wholegrain mustard or sweet and savoury tones of apple and sage jelly. Made with golden roasties, chicken thighs and fresh spring greens, it is hearty and wholesome - everything you need after a busy weekday.
